---
import { siteConfig } from '../config';
const giscus = siteConfig.giscus;
---

<section class="comments-panel liquid-card accent-cyan" aria-labelledby="comments-title">
  <div>
    <span class="eyebrow">DISCUSSION</span>
    <h2 id="comments-title">一起聊聊</h2>
  </div>
  {giscus.enabled && giscus.repo && giscus.repoId && giscus.categoryId ? (
    <script is:inline
      src="https://giscus.app/client.js"
      data-repo={giscus.repo}
      data-repo-id={giscus.repoId}
      data-category={giscus.category}
      data-category-id={giscus.categoryId}
      data-mapping="pathname"
      data-strict="0"
      data-reactions-enabled="1"
      data-emit-metadata="0"
      data-input-position="top"
      data-theme="transparent_dark"
      data-lang="zh-CN"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
      async
    ></script>
  ) : (
    <div class="comments-placeholder">
      <span>◌</span>
      <p>评论功能已预留。将网站仓库开启 GitHub Discussions，并在 <code>src/config.ts</code> 填入 Giscus 参数即可启用。</p>
    </div>
  )}
</section>
